name: crypt0_gal #2 - Unit:1477 - naughty cutie
description:
crypt0_gal NFT #2

Unit:1477 is a duplicate of Unit:1774. After learning how to produce clones of herself in the Metaverse, Unit:1774 started uploading around 10.000 different copies of herself into the digital space. Due to the circumstances of possible idependent evolution in digital life, all of her clones developed their own unique identities. Unit:1477 is a naughty girl, who loves to tempt people with her innocent appearance. She carries all the knowledge Unit:1774 collected until the cloning process though, which makes her someone to not to underestimate.
